column11: Combine meats and add to them the egg and half the seasonings
column12: Add half the cheese and mix meatball mix together
column13: Roll mixture into balls and place on tray
column14: Cut all tomatoes in half and chop the onion and pepper
column15: Place veggies and gnocci on tray with meatballs
column17: Bake until meatballs are 160 degrees. Sprinkle remaining cheese and serve
